description:
NrdcSnTermination: Table recording NRDC SN termination status for specific cells, including timestamps, location, cell identifiers, and termination status flags.

dateTime: Timestamp of the record.
Area_Name: Name of the geographical area where the cell is located.
CellId: Unique identifier for the cell.
Id2: Duplicate of CellId.
Id3: SN Termination status (e.g., prohibited).
vsDataType: Data type identifier.
vsDataFormatVersion: Version of the data format.
NrdcSnTermination.reservedBy: Reserved field.
NrdcSnTermination.defaultNrdcSnTerm: Flag indicating default SN termination status.
NrdcSnTermination.nrdcSnTerminationId: ID for the SN termination status.
